## Resolution Principle: Role-Based Adaptation

When personas conflict, the system adapts per role — not a forced compromise:
- Different default views per role
- Different density settings
- Different notification levels
- Different language levels
- Same system, different experience

## Adoption Priority

When in doubt, prioritize the role HARDEST to get to adopt:
{{ADOPTION_CHAIN}}

## Unresolvable Tensions

Some conflicts are PRODUCT DECISIONS, not UI decisions:
1. Label as "PRODUCT DECISION REQUIRED"
2. State the trade-off with business impact
3. Do NOT recommend — escalate to product owner

